      <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight">The Last Mile Just Got Shorter.</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">DoorDash is paying gig workers to film themselves doing chores. The footage trains robots to replace them. This is not new. It is just getting harder to ignore.</p>
